Kim Howe died in crash with Bruce Jenner on Pacific Coast Highway in February . 
  Her two stepchildren are said to have hired lawyers to look into possibility of wrongful death suit . 
  Close friends of Mrs Howe say she had 'virtually no relationship' with her stepchildren . 
  Mrs Howe was driving a white Lexus when she was rear-ended by Jenner . 
  Her stepchildren could be the only people to sue for wrongful death . 
  Jenner was not injured in the crash in Malibu, California . 
 